["cartservice-1", "adservice-0", "shippingservice-2", "checkoutservice-2", "recommendationservice-1", "currencyservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["paymentservice-2", "frontend-0", "currencyservice-0", "checkoutservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["productcatalogservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["frontend-1", "emailservice-2", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "emailservice-0", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["redis-cart-0", "recommendationservice-0", "adservice-2", "checkoutservice-0", "frontend-2", "paymentservice-0", "productcatalogservice-0"]}, "available_metric_names": ["client_error_ratio", "duration_99th", "error_ratio", "failed_query_ops", "memory_usage", "pod_cpu_usage", "rrt", "rrt_max", "server_error_ratio", "store_unhealth_count"], "log_analysis_findings": "基于对2025-06-28T00:10:09Z到2025-06-28T00:24:09Z期间系统日志的分析，我发现了显著的异常模式。以下是详细的分析结果：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\"Error 9005 (HY000)\", \"Region is unavailable\", \"rpc error\", \"failed to query product by id\", \"could not retrieve product\", \"failed to get product recommendations\", \"Unknown desc\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"数据库Region不可用导致产品查询失败，错误代码Error 9005 (HY000)\",\n      \"evidence\": \"productcatalogservice日志显示：\\\"failed to query product by id: Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\\\"，出现次数171次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"由于productcatalogservice的Region不可用错误，导致前端服务无法获取产品信息\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend日志显示：\\\"could not retrieve product: rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\\\"，出现次数最高达71次\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend\",\n      \"reason\": \"产品推荐服务依赖productcatalogservice失败，导致购物车功能异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"frontend日志显示：\\\"failed to get product recommendations: failed to get recommended product info (#VINTAGE123): rpc error: code = Unknown desc = Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable\\\"\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现：\n\n1. **主要故障模式**: 数据库Region不可用错误（Error 9005 (HY000)）\n2. **影响范围**: 涉及frontend和productcatalogservice两个服务\n3. **故障传播路径**: \n   - productcatalogservice首先出现数据库Region不可用错误\n   - frontend依赖productcatalogservice的产品查询功能，因此受到影响\n   - 导致产品展示、购物车、产品推荐等功能全面异常\n\n4. **严重程度**: productcatalogservice的错误日志出现172次，frontend的错误日志出现153次，表明这是一个严重的系统性故障。\n\n该故障的根本原因指向底层数据库服务的Region不可用问题，需要进一步检查数据库集群的状态和网络连接情况。", "trace_analysis_findings": "{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"rrt_max\",\n    \"frontend->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"frontend->checkoutservice\",\n    \"checkoutservice->productcatalogservice\",\n    \"error_ratio\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段平均耗时从正常时段的 9988.59 增加到 38585782.36，延迟倍数约为 3863 倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"状态码为 2，错误消息为 'Error 9005 (HY000): Region is unavailable'，出现次数为 120 次。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"rrt_max\",\n      \"evidence\": \"异常时段平均耗时从正常时段的 144331.80 增加到 40290515.50，延迟倍数约为 279 倍。\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"error_ratio\",\n      \"evidence\": \"状态码为 13，错误消息为 'failed to prepare order: failed to get product'，出现次数为 2 次。\"\n    }\n  ]\n}", "metric_analysis_findings": "基于收集到的故障期间指标数据，我已经完成了初始扫描分析。以下是发现的显著异常情况：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"duration_99th\", \"rrt_max\", \"rrt\", \"error_ratio\", \"server_error_ratio\", \"client_error_ratio\", \"failed_query_ops\", \"memory_usage\", \"store_unhealth_count\", \"pod_cpu_usage\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-tidb\",\n      \"reason\": \"TiDB数据库出现严重性能问题，duration_99th从0.01ms飙升到64.88ms，同时memory_usage异常变化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"duration_99th变化率199.94%，memory_usage从1.01GB降至564MB，failed_query_ops的p99从0增加到14.67\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"产品目录服务响应时间急剧恶化，rrt_max从12.5秒飙升至4027.7万秒，同时error_ratio达到60%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max变化率199.88%，error_ratio从0%升至60%，client_error_ratio同样达到60%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"productcatalogservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"产品目录服务实例响应时间显著增加，rrt从7.4秒增至1689.2万秒\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt变化率199.83%，p99值从7.6秒增至2092.4万秒\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务出现严重错误，server_error_ratio和error_ratio均达到26.32%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio从0%升至26.32%，error_ratio同样异常，p99值达到35.55%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"前端服务实例错误率异常，server_error_ratio和error_ratio均为12.96%\",\n      \"evidence\": \"server_error_ratio和error_ratio从0%升至12.96%，p99值达到29.57%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"tidb-pd\",\n      \"reason\": \"TiDB PD组件出现存储健康问题，store_unhealth_count异常\",\n      \"evidence\": \"store_unhealth_count的p99值从0增加到1.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"结账服务响应时间异常，rrt的p99值从8.6秒增至2417.0万秒\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt的p99变化率199.86%，client_error_ratio的p99达到33.54%\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis缓存服务CPU使用率异常变化\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage的p99值从0.12降至0，可能存在重启或异常状态\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n**关键发现总结：**\n1. **TiDB数据库集群**出现严重性能问题，响应时间飙升6400倍\n2. **产品目录服务**是受影响最严重的应用服务，响应时间异常且错误率极高\n3. **前端服务**出现大量服务器错误，影响用户体验\n4. **多个微服务**出现连锁反应，表明可能存在级联故障\n5. **Redis缓存服务**CPU使用异常，可能影响数据访问性能\n\n这些异常主要集中在数据库层和应用服务层，需要进一步分析确定根本原因。"}
